8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Integrately and Kissflow share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. On the other hand, Kissflow uniquely offers Code Support and Error Handling and Team Collaboration, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Integrately holds an overall score of 6/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Kissflow scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Integrately offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Free, compared to Kissflow's starting price of $1500/mo. Integrately has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Kissflow does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
