c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Integrately is best suited for non technical users, small businesses, quick setups, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Kissflow, meanwhile, shines for mid market companies, process owners, HR teams, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2019, Integrately describes itself as \"One-click automation platform with ready-made integration recipes.\" Kissflow, established in 2012, positions itself as \"Low-code work platform for process automation and project management.\" With 7 years between them, Kissflow brings the maturity and proven track record of a veteran platform, while Integrately offers the fresh perspective and modern architecture of a newer entrant."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Kissflow** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to more features (9 vs 6). However, this does not mean Integrately is a poor choice — far from it. Integrately excels in its own right, particularly for non technical users and small businesses.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value combines workflow and project management, go with Kissflow. If extremely easy one-click setup matters more to you, Integrately is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
